        "tags": [
          "A – Simple distinct bugs"
        ],
        "summary": "Divide two integers",
        "description": "BUG-001 — divide-by-zero style crash.\nTriggered when denominator == 0.\nSimple, isolated bug; expected to form a clean singleton cluster.",
