        "summary": "Strict item lookup",
        "description": "BUG-009 — returns HTTP 400 with oracle header for item_id == 0.\nThe OpenAPI spec documents a normal success response; a fuzzer configured to\ntreat unexpected 400s as validation-style crashes should flag this.\nThis tests whether the deduplicator handles non-5xx crashes correctly.",
        "operationId": "strict_item_strict__item_id__get",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "item_id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
